Proposed timetable:
# TravelPlan: Relaxed Marrakech riad trip for 2 from Hamburg, 5–12 July 2026

| Day 1 — 2026-07-05 — Arrival in Marrakech | Day 2 — 2026-07-06 — Medina orientation and souks | Day 3 — 2026-07-07 — Palaces and Jewish Quarter | Day 4 — 2026-07-08 — Gardens and architecture | Day 5 — 2026-07-09 — Madrasa and museum day | Day 6 — 2026-07-10 — Food markets and cooking | Day 7 — 2026-07-11 — Relaxed hammam and farewell | Day 8 — 2026-07-12 — Departure to Hamburg |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1. Light pre-flight lunch in Hamburg** [meal] 12:30–13:30 @ Hamburg / Hamburg Airport (€35.00) — Keep the first day gentle before the late flight: a light lunch at home or near Hamburg Airport, with hydration and electrolytes prepared for Marrakech heat. | **1. Taxi to Barcelona overnight hotel** [transport] 00:50–01:20 @ Barcelona El Prat Airport → central Barcelona hotel (€35.00) — Short taxi after landing to a pre-booked hotel so the overnight layover is spent in a bed rather than in the airport terminal. | **1. Breakfast at the riad** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Riad Tamarrakecht (€0.00) — Included Moroccan breakfast in the riad courtyard before an early guided history morning. — Links: [link 1](https://www.riadtamarrakecht.com/en/) | **1. Early riad breakfast** [meal] 07:00–07:35 @ Riad Tamarrakecht (€0.00) — Early breakfast before a timed garden visit. — Links: [link 1](https://www.riadtamarrakecht.com/en/) | **1. Breakfast at the riad** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Riad Tamarrakecht (€0.00) — Slow riad breakfast before a northern Medina architecture morning. — Links: [link 1](https://www.riadtamarrakecht.com/en/) | **1. Breakfast at the riad** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Riad Tamarrakecht (€0.00) — Breakfast before the food-market and cooking experience. — Links: [link 1](https://www.riadtamarrakecht.com/en/) | **1. Breakfast at the riad** [meal] 08:30–09:15 @ Riad Tamarrakecht (€0.00) — A relaxed final full-day breakfast with no early start. — Links: [link 1](https://www.riadtamarrakecht.com/en/) | **1. Check out and private airport transfer** [transport] 04:15–04:45 @ Riad Tamarrakecht → Marrakech Menara Airport (€25.00) — Pre-booked transfer to Marrakech Menara Airport for the verified return flight. Although the departure remains early because live search returned this as the available/cheapest return, the transfer is shifted later than before and the previous day is kept very light. Ask the riad for porter help and a breakfast box. — Links: [link 1](https://www.riadtamarrakecht.com/en/) |
| **2. Early dinner before airport security** [meal] 18:00–19:00 @ Hamburg Airport (HAM) (€30.00) — Early light dinner before security so the late evening connection is less tiring. | **2. Barcelona overnight hotel — TOC Hotel Las Ramblas** [lodging] 01:20–05:45 @ TOC Hotel Las Ramblas, Barcelona (€177.00) — Overnight rest during the Barcelona connection, replacing the physically demanding airport layover. Live hotel search returned TOC Hotel Las Ramblas at €177/night for 2 adults; request elevator-access room and arrange rapid check-in. — Links: [link 1](https://travelstack.nuitee.link/hotels/lp5793a?checkin=2026-07-05&checkout=2026-07-06&rooms=1&adults=2&occupancies=W3siYWR1bHRzIjoyLCJjaGlsZHJlbiI6W119XQ%3D%3D&language=de&currency=EUR) | **2. Guided Bahia Palace, Mellah and Saadian Tombs tour** [attraction] 09:00–12:30 @ Bahia Palace, Mellah, Saadian Tombs, Marrakech (€110.00) — Relaxed private/small-group historical architecture morning with Bahia Palace, Place des Ferblantiers/Mellah context, and Saadian Tombs. Sites open around 09:00–17:00; early visit avoids heat and crowds. — Links: [link 1](https://www.google.com/maps/search/Marrakech+WITH+Locals), [link 2](https://bahiapalace.com/), [link 3](https://morocco-phototours.com/saadian-tombs-marrakech-opening-hours/) | **2. Taxi to Jardin Majorelle** [transport] 07:35–07:55 @ Riad Tamarrakecht → Jardin Majorelle (€5.00) — Taxi to Majorelle at opening; route is about 2.3 km and 4–10 minutes depending on traffic, but allow extra time. — Links: [link 1](https://www.jardinmajorelle.com/en/) | **2. Walk/taxi to Ben Youssef area** [transport] 08:45–09:00 @ Riad Tamarrakecht → Ben Youssef Madrasa area (€5.00) — Short transfer or shaded walk to Ben Youssef Square; use a taxi to Place de Moukef if already hot. | **2. Taxi to cooking class meeting point** [transport] 09:15–09:35 @ Riad Tamarrakecht → Art Darmed / Sidi Abdelaziz area (€5.00) — Short taxi/escorted walk to the cooking-class venue to avoid getting lost in the 